sentence: what are the highest points of states surrounding mississippi ?
sentence-with-vars: what are the highest points of states surrounding state0 ?
sql: select highlow.highest_point from highlow where highlow.state_name in ( select border_info.border from border_info where border_info.state_name = ' mississippi ' ) ;
sql-with-vars: select highlow.highest_point from highlow where highlow.state_name in ( select border_info.border from border_info where border_info.state_name = ' state0 ' ) ;
